description:
Experience unrivaled strength, space, and luxury with the 2026 Ram 2500 Limited Mega Cab 4x4, finished in Bright White Clear Coat and powered by the legendary 6.7L I6 Cummins High Output Turbo Diesel. Built for those who demand uncompromising capability and premium comfort, this heavy-duty truck is ready for work, play, and everything in between.

Beneath the hood, the high-output Cummins Turbo Diesel is paired with an 8-speed TorqueFlite HD automatic transmission and a 3.42 rear axle ratio, delivering immense towing power and performance. The Off-Road Package adds front and rear performance-tuned shock absorbers, hill descent control, and a transfer case skid-plate shield for rugged trail capability. A 5th wheel and gooseneck towing prep group, Class V receiver hitch, trailer reverse guidance, and trailer tire pressure monitoring system ensure you are ready for the heaviest hauls with maximum control.

This Mega Cab offers expansive rear legroom and extra storage while the Limited Level 1 Equipment Group enhances safety and convenience with features like surround-view camera, adaptive steering, digital rearview mirror, drowsy driver detection, active lane management, traffic sign recognition, and power deployable running boards. The power sunroof, clearance lamps, and deployable Mopar bed step with spray-in bedliner provide added visibility and usability.

Inside, ultra premium leather seats in Black with Ebony Red accents set the tone for a refined cabin. Heated and ventilated front seats, heated second-row seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, heated steering wheel, and power-adjustable pedals with memory ensure comfort for every drive. Dual wireless charging pads and a 12-inch color cluster display provide high-tech functionality.

The Uconnect 5 NAV system features a massive 14.4-inch touchscreen, front passenger interactive display, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, SiriusXM 360L, and a 17-speaker Harman Kardon premium audio system for immersive sound on the go.

With a 10,000-pound GVWR rating and a 31-gallon fuel tank, this 2026 Ram 2500 Limited Mega Cab 4x4 is built for endurance. Assembled in Saltillo Mexico and backed by a 5-year or 100000-mile powertrain limited warranty and a 3-year or 36000-mile basic limited warranty, this truck is built to dominate. MyFlexCare Service is also included. This is luxury that leads and muscle that moves.
